          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "Is it safe for anxious or first-time pets?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Yes — the safety blade guard controls how much nail can enter the cutting zone, and the quiet, precise cut keeps stress low. 96% of pet parents noticed less stress during nail cutting.</p>",
