            "heading": "Does it work for both dogs and cats?",
            "icon": "check_box",
            "filled_icon": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely. The clipper is designed for dogs and cats of all sizes — small paws to large breeds.</p>",
            "page": ""
          },
          "blocks": {}
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "collapsible-row-content",
          "settings": {
            "open": false,
            "heading": "What about dark nails where I can’t see the quick?",
            "icon": "check_box",
